{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778468851257,"sessionID":"ses_1eb0738caffeL99d0ei3NGmrjL","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"bash","callID":"functions.bash:74","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"command":"git commit -m \"NTR: Add double-stranded RNA immune receptor activity and left-handed Z-RNA immune receptor activity terms\n\nAdded two new terms as requested in issue #32046:\n\n- GO:7770072 double-stranded RNA immune receptor activity\n  Child of GO:0038187 pattern recognition receptor activity.\n  Definition: Combining with a double-stranded RNA and transmitting the signal\n  to initiate an innate immune response.\n  Includes logical definition: signaling receptor activity that has_primary_input\n  CHEBI:67208 (double-stranded RNA) and has_part GO:0003725 (double-stranded RNA binding).\n  Synonym: dsRNA immune receptor activity.\n  Provenance: PMID:33243852, PMID:34678144, PMID:23273991.\n\n- GO:7770073 left-handed Z-RNA immune receptor activity\n  Child of GO:7770072 double-stranded RNA immune receptor activity.\n  Definition: Combining with a left-handed Z-RNA and transmitting the signal\n  to initiate an innate immune response.\n  Does not have a CHEBI-based logical definition as no Z-RNA CHEBI term exists;\n  placed under the dsRNA parent by is_a with has_part double-stranded RNA binding.\n  Synonym: Z-RNA immune receptor activity.\n  Provenance: PMID:32200799.\n\nBoth terms include term_tracker_item links to issue #32046.\n\ncloses #32046\"","description":"Commit the new terms"},"output":"[scribe-v1-ai4curation-go-ontology-agent-config-v9-.-togetherai-moonshotai-Kimi-K2.6-iter1-issue-32046 c5045e3] NTR: Add double-stranded RNA immune receptor activity and left-handed Z-RNA immune receptor activity terms\n 1 file changed, 26 insertions(+)\n","metadata":{"output":"[scribe-v1-ai4curation-go-ontology-agent-config-v9-.-togetherai-moonshotai-Kimi-K2.6-iter1-issue-32046 c5045e3] NTR: Add double-stranded RNA immune receptor activity and left-handed Z-RNA immune receptor activity terms\n 1 file changed, 26 insertions(+)\n","exit":0,"description":"Commit the new terms","truncated":false},"title":"Commit the new terms","time":{"start":1778468851252,"end":1778468851256}},"id":"prt_e1500e158001Rdtps46jsxcD1y","sessionID":"ses_1eb0738caffeL99d0ei3NGmrjL","messageID":"msg_e1500c85c001wqd13Vfi5561rf"}}
