{"type":"text","timestamp":1778468925370,"sessionID":"ses_1eb0738caffeL99d0ei3NGmrjL","part":{"id":"prt_e15020807001OP4HzLp5Aey15K","messageID":"msg_e1501fcdc001tgWznEe7xImIO5","sessionID":"ses_1eb0738caffeL99d0ei3NGmrjL","type":"text","text":"All done. Here's a summary of what was completed:\n\n- **Analyzed issue #32046**: Request for two new terms â€” `double-stranded RNA immune receptor activity` and `left-handed Z-RNA immune receptor activity`.\n- **Pre-validated** the ontology (`robot convert` passed cleanly).\n- **Researched and validated** the four provided PMIDs via NCBI (all are real and biologically relevant).\n- **Consulted existing terms and design patterns** for `pattern recognition receptor activity` children, confirming the standard CHEBI-based logical definition pattern.\n- **Created two new terms**:\n  - **GO:7770072** `double-stranded RNA immune receptor activity`  \n    - `is_a: GO:0038187` with full logical definition using `CHEBI:67208` (double-stranded RNA), which already exists in GOâ€™s import closure.\n    - `has_part GO:0003725` (double-stranded RNA binding)\n    - Synonym: *dsRNA immune receptor activity*\n    - Provenance: PMID:33243852, PMID:34678144, PMID:23273991\n  - **GO:7770073** `left-handed Z-RNA immune receptor activity`\n    - `is_a: GO:7770072` (no CHEBI term exists for Z-RNA, so no logical definition was added â€” consistent with other GO terms where an external differentia is missing).\n    - `has_part GO:0003725` (double-stranded RNA binding)\n    - Synonym: *Z-RNA immune receptor activity*\n    - Provenance: PMID:32200799\n- **Checked terms in** using `obo-checkin.pl`.\n- **Post-edit validation**:\n  - `robot convert` â€” passed\n  - `robot reason` (ELK) â€” passed, no unsatisfiable classes\n  - SPARQL checks (missing namespace, duplicate synonyms, obsolete defs, definition constraints) â€” all 0 violations\n- **Committed** `src/ontology/go-edit.obo` with a detailed commit message.\n- **Created** `ISSUE_COMMENTS.md` and `PR_COMMENTS.md` in the repository root (not committed).","time":{"start":1778468915207,"end":1778468925369}}}
